Ex-Polycom Executive to Pay $85,000 on Insider Trading Claims

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-09-21T20:47:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/ex-polycom-executive-to-pay-85-000-on-insider-trading-claims.html
Sunil Bhalla, a former executive at
 Polycom Inc. (PLCM) , agreed to pay $85,000 as part of a settlement of
claims tied to  insider trading , the Securities and Exchange
Commission said in a statement on its website.  Bhalla provided nonpublic data to  Roomy Khan , with the
information leading to $2.5 million in illicit trading gains,
according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  